    "created_at": "2023-05-05T17:36:18Z",
    "updated_at": "2023-05-05T17:36:18Z",
    "body": "I believe those options have been removed in 2020 with [starship v0.45.0](https://starship.rs/migrating-to-0.45.0/).\r\n\r\n[The git status options](https://starship.rs/config/#git-status) now use format strings that can access a `$count` variable, for example:\r\n```toml\r\n[git_status]\r\nahead = '⇡${count}'\r\ndiverged = '⇕⇡${ahead_count}⇣${behind_count}'\r\nbehind = '⇣${count}'\r\n```",
